sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor U as User/Frontend
participant API as FastAPI Route
participant S as In-Memory Store
participant BG as BackgroundTasks
participant A as Agent Runner
participant P as Playwright
participant G as Gemini API
participant IO as Socket.IO Server

U->>API: POST /api/test/ {url, focus}
API->>API: Validate TestRequest
API->>API: Generate test_id
API->>S: set(test_id, TestRun{status=running})
API->>BG: add_task(run_agent, test_id, url, focus, sio)
API-->>U: 200 {id, status=running}

par Live channel setup
U->>IO: connect with query testId
IO->>IO: enter_room(sid, test_id)
and Background execution
BG->>A: run_agent(...)
A->>A: run_in_executor(_run_agent_sync)

A->>S: get(test_id)
A->>P: launch chromium + new page
A->>P: goto(url)
A->>P: screenshot
A->>S: add_action(navigate)
A->>IO: emit action (navigate)

loop Up to 50 turns
A->>P: screenshot current page
A->>G: generate_content(prompt + screenshot)
G-->>A: JSON decision {action, args, reasoning}
A->>A: parse_json_response

alt action == done
A->>P: screenshot final state
A->>S: add_action(done)
A->>IO: emit action (done)
A->>A: break loop
else executable action
A->>P: execute_single_action(action, args)
A->>P: wait_for_load_state + settle
A->>P: screenshot after action
A->>S: add_action(action)
A->>IO: emit action(action)
else parse failed
A->>A: skip turn and retry
end
end

alt turn limit reached
A->>P: screenshot timeout state
A->>S: add_action(done: timeout)
A->>IO: emit action(done: timeout)
end

A->>S: update(status=complete, completed_at)
A->>IO: emit complete
end

opt client polling fallback
U->>API: GET /api/test/{test_id}
API->>S: get(test_id)
API-->>U: TestRun (status/actions/cases)
end

opt fetch only cases
U->>API: GET /api/test/{test_id}/cases
API->>S: get(test_id)
API-->>U: {test_id, cases}
end

alt exception anywhere in agent
A->>P: try screenshot (if possible)
A->>S: add_action(done: error)
A->>IO: emit action(done:error)
A->>S: update(status=failed)
A->>IO: emit error
end
